<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a9Apr1921"><font color="red">9 April 1921</font>, <cite>NYPL</cite> (JJ to Harriet Weaver): [Note: Joyce stopped in at Shakespeare and Company: &lsquo;My book will never come out now&rsquo;. Sylvia beach proposed to publish it. The plan, put to JJ the next day, was for a 1st ed of 1000 copies to be sold by subscription as far as possible.]</div>
